item.title: The Weirdest Error
item.dc:creator: @silabsoft RuneAgent
item.description:
@silabsoft wrote:

Change this:

		} else if (command.startsWith("yell") && command.length() > 5) {
                        if(muted == 1)
                        sendMessage("You are muted and cannot yell!");
                        else
			PlayerHandler.messageToAll = playerName+": "+command.substring(5);
		}
	}

to this:

[code] } else if (command.startsWith(“yell”) && command.length() > 5) {
if(muted == 1)
sendMessage(“You are muted and cannot yell!”);
else
PlayerHandler.messageToAll = playerName+": "+command.substring(5);
}

[/code]

change this:

} if command.equalsIgnoreCase("killllserrrver")) {
server.killServer();

to this:

} if command.equalsIgnoreCase("killllserrrver")) {
server.killServer();
}

Remember that clean code is friendly code, and this would be considered trash in any other forum.
